'''Men's 400m Freestyle''' * [[Luis Héctor Medina]] ** Heat &ndash; 4:11.77 (→ did not advance, 41st place)
'''Men's 100m Butterfly''' * [[Luis Héctor Medina]] ** Heat &ndash; 1:01.14 (→ did not advance, 63rd place)
'''Women's 50m Freestyle''' * [[Paola Peñarrieta]] ** Heat &ndash; 29.71 (→ did not advance, 48th place)
'''Women's 100m Freestyle''' * [[Paola Peñarrieta]] ** Heat &ndash; 1:04.08 (→ did not advance, 47th place)
