{{Distinguish|Virgin Islands Olympic Committee}} {{Infobox National Olympic Committee | title = British Virgin Islands Olympic Committee | logo = British Virgin Islands Olympic Committee logo.jpg | size = 150px | country = British Virgin Islands | code = IVB | created = 1980 | recognized = 1982 | association = PASO | headquarters = | president = Ephraim Penn | secretary general = Dean Greenaway | website = [http://www.bviolympics.org bviolympics.org] }}
The '''British Virgin Islands Olympic Committee''' (IOC code: '''IVB''') is the [[National Olympic Committee]] representing the [[British Virgin Islands]]. It is also the body responsible for the British Virgin Islands's representation at the [[Commonwealth Games]].<ref>{{cite web|title=British Virgin Islands at the Commonwealth Games|url=http://www.thecgf.com/countries/intro.asp?countryid=13|publisher=[[Commonwealth Games Federation]]|accessdate=17 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201651/http://www.thecgf.com/countries/intro.asp?countryid=13#|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref>
