{{infobox country at games | NPC = NOR | NPCname = [[Norwegian Olympic and Paralympic Committee and Confederation of Sports]] | games = Winter Paralympics | year = 1994 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.idrett.no }}&nbsp;{{no icon}} | location = [[Lillehammer]] | competitors = 43 | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = 1 | gold = 29 | silver = 22 | bronze = 13 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Norway]]''' competed at the '''[[1994 Winter Paralympics]]''' in [[Lillehammer]], [[Norway]]. 43 competitors from Norway won 64 medals including 29 gold, 22 silver and 13 bronze and finished 1st in the [[1994 Winter Paralympics medal table|medal table]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/norway|title=Norway - National Paralympic Committee|website=www.paralympic.org|access-date=2016-06-16}}</ref>
