{{Infobox national volleyball team | name = Sri Lanka | gender = men | image = Flag of Sri Lanka.svg | federation = [[Sri Lanka Volleyball Federation]] | website = | confederation = AVC | manager = | coach = DEJAN VULIĆEVIĆ (Serbia) ]] }}
The '''Sri Lanka men's national volleyball team''' represents Sri Lanka in international volleyball competitions and friendly matches. The team is currently ranked 78th in the world.<ref>[http://www.fivb.org/en/volleyball/VB_Ranking_M_2012-07.asp FIVB World Rankings]</ref>
