{{Infobox football league | logo = | pixels = | caption = | country = {{flagicon|East Timor}} [[Timor Leste]] | confed = [[Asian Football Confederation|AFC]] | founded = {{Start date and age|2005}} | folded = 2010 | teams = 9 | promotion = [[Super Liga Timorense]] | relegation = | levels = | domest_cup = | confed_cup = | champions = | most successful club = | sponsorship_name = | tv = [[Radio-Televisão Timor Leste|TVTL]] | current = }} '''Timorense Liga Pre'''<ref>[http://rsssf.com/tableso/oosttim06.html East Timor 2005/06]</ref> is the second division of the [[Federaçao Futebol Timor-Leste]]. This competition is a qualification for [[Super Liga Timorense]], the first division. The competition was replaced by [[Liga Futebol Amadora Segunda Divisão]].
==Format== This competition format using the system home tournament, divided into 2 (two) groups consisting of 4-5 clubs each.
